headline: Chime debut, ConAgra downgrade, Cardinal Health lifts outlook
summary: Yahoo Finance host Josh Lipton tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute. Chime (CHYM) debuts on the Nasdaq Composite (^IXIC), opening at $43 per share. ConAgra Brands (CAG) was downgraded to Underperform from Neutral by BofA Securities and lowered its price target to $20 from $27. Cardinal Health (CAH) stock is rising after lifting its earnings outlook for the full year. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
